<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.4">
<l>ācai vaḻuvā tēttu memakkiṅ kiḻukkāyt taṭiyōrkkut</l>
<l>tēca maṟiya vumakkē yāḷāyt tirikiṉ ṟōmukku</l>
<l>kāci ṉoḷiyil tikaḻum vaṇṇam kāṭṭī remperumāṉ</l>
<l>vāci vallī rinta ḷūrīr vāḻntē pōmnīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For us here who praise [you] without fail, longing has become a fault.</l>
<l>To us who are your devotees, to us who are wandering as servants to only you</l>
<l rend="indent">so the [whole] country knows,</l>
<l>You do not show your beauty which shines more than the glitter of coins.</l>
<l>Our lord, you are one who can do what is right. You of Intaḷūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">live happily!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
